data.title: Rainbow Recreation Center
data.meta_description: The official website of the City of Oakland. Find out about meetings, request City services through OAK 311, or contact the Mayor and City Council.
data.text:
Facility Rentals - We are always available for special events like: birthday parties, baby showers, business meetings, etc.

Reservations must be made 30 days in advance of the event.

Open Gyms - Please call our recreation center for hours, times may change per season.

Fall and Spring availability: Monday - Friday 11am - 2pm

No availability during the summer months
